OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1771959890
OL,3,CMedical student charged with accessing
OL,4,Cthe personal data of 46 patients
OL,6,FA medical student in Guernsey has been
OL,7,Faccused of illegally accessing the
OL,8,Fpersonal data of 46 patients which is
OL,9,Fbelieved to have happened whilst she
OL,10,Fwas working at the Princess Elizabeth
OL,11,FHospital.
OL,13,FRebecca Elliot, 35, appeared at the
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court this morning
OL,15,Fcharged with eight offences relating
OL,16,Fto the island's Data Protection Laws.
OL,18,FShe spoke only to confirm her name and
OL,19,Faddress and has not yet submitted a
OL,20,Fformal plea.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
