FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1771959890
OL,3,CMedical student charged with accessing
OL,4,Cthe personal data of 46 patients
OL,6,FIt is alleged her offending took place
OL,7,Fover the course of six years from
OL,8,FOctober 2019 to October 2025.
OL,10,FDuring that period, it is understood
OL,11,Fshe obtained the data "knowingly or
OL,12,Frecklessly, without the consent of the
OL,13,Fdata controller."
OL,15,FThe States of Guernsey have confirmed
OL,16,Fshe has been suspended as a member of
OL,17,Fstaff following the active
OL,18,Finvestigation into her conduct.
OL,26,@sD@WOU
