OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1771959890
OL,3,CMedical student charged with accessing
OL,4,Cthe personal data of 46 patients
OL,6,FElaine Burgess, Director of Care
OL,7,FDelivery, said: "We have notified the
OL,8,Faffected individuals and offered
OL,9,Fsupport, informed the Office of the
OL,10,FData Protection Authority and referred
OL,11,Fthe matter to the police.
OL,13,F"We recognise how upsetting and
OL,14,Funsettling this incident has been for
OL,15,Fthose affected, however, as this
OL,16,Fmatter is now before the courts, we
OL,17,Fcannot comment further to avoid
OL,18,Fprejudicing active legal proceedings."
OL,26,@zD@fO]
