CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1771959890
OL,3,CMedical student charged with accessing
OL,4,Cthe personal data of 46 patients
OL,6,FThe Office for Data Protection say
OL,7,Fthey are unable to comment on this
OL,8,Flive investigation, however, have
OL,9,Fconfirmed that they have been made
OL,10,Faware of the breach.
OL,12,FMs Elliot will next appear in court on
OL,13,F9 March.
